  "detailed_description": "CaS-Puz is a 3D puzzle platformer where everything is based on the position of the camera. You look at the wall from one side — it exists. You look from the other — you can go through it. But you have to open and close them for your own purposes.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2518250/extras/6fe66277cff4b096a12ff74170140678.poster.avif?t=1736536784\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2518250/extras/6fe66277cff4b096a12ff74170140678.webm?t=1736536784\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2518250/extras/6fe66277cff4b096a12ff74170140678.mp4?t=1736536784\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>However, you can't stand on open walls, and you can't jump away from them. During maneuvers, you will have to both open and close many walls.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2518250/extras/53e6ea51fbaa50d08ce0721cccfdada5.poster.avif?t=1736536784\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2518250/extras/53e6ea51fbaa50d08ce0721cccfdada5.webm?t=1736536784\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2518250/extras/53e6ea51fbaa50d08ce0721cccfdada5.mp4?t=1736536784\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Easy to learn — hard to master.</strong> The controls are straightforward and standard — relative to the camera. Just to keep the direction of movement, you will have to change controls on the fly. <br><br><strong>A puzzle and a platformer.</strong> Before you make a jump, look around and think. Understand the correct sequence of jumps and camera turns.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2518250/extras/967661ed4777498e1b27c5133da88f77.poster.avif?t=1736536784\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2518250/extras/967661ed4777498e1b27c5133da88f77.webm?t=1736536784\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2518250/extras/967661ed4777498e1b27c5133da88f77.mp4?t=1736536784\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>If you are a fan of hardcore platformers, then in CaS-Puz you will definitely find a new challenge for yourself.",
  "about_the_game": "CaS-Puz is a 3D puzzle platformer where everything is based on the position of the camera. You look at the wall from one side — it exists. You look from the other — you can go through it. But you have to open and close them for your own purposes.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2518250/extras/6fe66277cff4b096a12ff74170140678.poster.avif?t=1736536784\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2518250/extras/6fe66277cff4b096a12ff74170140678.webm?t=1736536784\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2518250/extras/6fe66277cff4b096a12ff74170140678.mp4?t=1736536784\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>However, you can't stand on open walls, and you can't jump away from them. During maneuvers, you will have to both open and close many walls.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2518250/extras/53e6ea51fbaa50d08ce0721cccfdada5.poster.avif?t=1736536784\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2518250/extras/53e6ea51fbaa50d08ce0721cccfdada5.webm?t=1736536784\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2518250/extras/53e6ea51fbaa50d08ce0721cccfdada5.mp4?t=1736536784\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Easy to learn — hard to master.</strong> The controls are straightforward and standard — relative to the camera. Just to keep the direction of movement, you will have to change controls on the fly. <br><br><strong>A puzzle and a platformer.</strong> Before you make a jump, look around and think. Understand the correct sequence of jumps and camera turns.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2518250/extras/967661ed4777498e1b27c5133da88f77.poster.avif?t=1736536784\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2518250/extras/967661ed4777498e1b27c5133da88f77.webm?t=1736536784\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2518250/extras/967661ed4777498e1b27c5133da88f77.mp4?t=1736536784\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>If you are a fan of hardcore platformers, then in CaS-Puz you will definitely find a new challenge for yourself.",
